\c 1
\s Kufara kwavanoda Mwari, nokusafara kwavasingadi Mwari
\p
\v 1 Akakomborerwa munhu asingafambi panorangana vakaipa, Asingamiri panzira yavatadzi, Asingagari panogara vadadi.
\v 2 Asi anofarira murayiro waJehovha; Anofungisisa murayiro wake masikati nousiku.
\v 3 Achafanana nomuti wakasimwa pahova dzemvura, Anobereka michero yawo nenguva yawo, Mashizha awo haasvavi; Chinhu chipi nechipi chaanoita chichaendika.
\v 4 Vakaipa havana kudaro; Asi vakafanana nehundi inopepereswa nemhepo.
\v 5 Naizvozvo vakaipa havangamiri pakutongeswa, Navatadzi paungano yavakarurama.
\v 6 Nokuti Jehovha anoziva nzira yavakarurama; Asi nzira yavakaipa ichaparadzwa.
